   \"age\": \"fresh\",\n        \"label\": \"status=active; staleness=fresh; source_anchor=untracked\",\n        \"source_anchor\": \"untracked\",\n        \"status\": \"active\"\n      },\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"June 18 GitHub queue cleanup for PRs 527, 529, 531\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"github-queue-2026-06-18-pr527-pr531\",\n      \"type\": \"bugfix\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-06-18 14:18\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 79304,\n      \"preview\": \"PR #110 (`Tighten threads run logging and merge gates`) was merged on 2026-06-24T09:33:16Z with merge commit `05fee6aaf030396cc78d7fbd1f937785c6f0ec73`, closing issue #107 at 2026-06-24T09:33:17Z. The final head before merge was `f75a324e2bb03c823f53ca8c0b0722155abb462e`. Three Codex review threads \",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/AI/tools/claude-arsenal\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"staleness\": {\n        \"age\": \"fresh\",\n        \"label\": \"status=active; staleness=fresh; source_anchor=untracked\",\n        \"source_anchor\": \"untracked\",\n        \"status\": \"active\"\n      },\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"PR #110 merged after resolving connector merge-gate review threads\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"threads-pr110-delayed-review-recheck\",\n      \"type\": \"bugfix\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-06-24 09:33\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 79299,\n      \"preview\": \"On 2026-06-17, after user requested non-GUI cleanup work via threads, created GitHub issues #156-#163 for remaining non-GUI rclean gaps. Implemented two PRs from origin/main bf62d996: PR #165 fixes #156 by making `clean --plan` honor ActionPlan `deleteMode`, rejecting conflicting CLI mode flags, and\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/AI/tools/rclean\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"staleness\": {\n        \"age\": \"fresh\",\n        \"label\": \"status=active; s